5:["$","main",null,{"children":["$","article",null,{"className":"pt-32 md:pt-40 pb-24 px-6 md:px-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"rs-eyebrow","style":{"fontSize":"0.7rem","color":"#D22C2E"},"children":["Kitchen economics · ","2026-06-12"," · ",5," min read"]}],["$","h1",null,{"className":"rs-display mt-4","style":{"fontSize":"clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 3rem)","lineHeight":1.1,"fontWeight":600,"color":"#2A160C"},"children":"Why batch codes make kitchen audits painless"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-8 grid gap-5","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"rs-body","style":{"color":"#4A3728","fontSize":"1.02rem","lineHeight":1.85},"children":"Every kitchen dreads the audit week — FSSAI inspections, brand audits for franchises, hygiene certifications for institutional contracts. The spice shelf is a classic stumbling block: loose-ground masalas in unmarked dabbas, with no answer to the simplest question an auditor asks — 'where did this come from?'"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"rs-body","style":{"color":"#4A3728","fontSize":"1.02rem","lineHeight":1.85},"children":"Batch coding answers it in one line. A batch-coded pack ties the blend in your kitchen to a specific production run, and that run to specific lab-checked raw lots — chilli from a named mandi purchase, turmeric from a specific polishing lot. Provenance stops being a story and becomes a lookup."}],["$","p","2",{"className":"rs-body","style":{"color":"#4A3728","fontSize":"1.02rem","lineHeight":1.85},"children":"For the kitchen, the practical wins are concrete: expiry management is automatic (the code carries the packing date), complaints become traceable (one odd batch can be isolated instead of condemning the whole shelf), and audit documentation is a photograph of a label rather than an afternoon of reconstruction."}],["$","p","3",{"className":"rs-body","style":{"color":"#4A3728","fontSize":"1.02rem","lineHeight":1.85},"children":"For institutional and export buyers, batch-coded supply with a per-batch certificate of analysis is increasingly not a differentiator but a ticket to entry. Rail caterers, hospital kitchens and modern-trade private labels simply will not onboard suppliers without it."}],["$","p","4",{"className":"rs-body","style":{"color":"#4A3728","fontSize":"1.02rem","lineHeight":1.85},"children":"If your current masala arrives in unmarked polythene, that is not a price advantage — it is an audit liability with a delivery schedule."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-12 rounded-2xl p-7","style":{"background":"rgba(250,162,25,0.12)","border":"1px solid rgba(250,162,25,0.4)"},"children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"rs-display","style":{"fontSize":"1.2rem","color":"#2A160C","fontWeight":600},"children":"Run the numbers on your own menu."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"rs-body mt-2","style":{"color":"#6B5040","fontSize":"0.92rem"},"children":"The cost-per-plate calculator on our products page uses the same math as this article."}],["$","$L10",null,{"href":"/products","className":"rs-btn inline-block mt-5 px-6 py-3 rounded-full","style":{"background":"#D22C2E","color":"#fff","fontSize":"0.75rem"},"children":"Open the calculator"}]]}],["$","$L10",null,{"href":"/blog","className":"rs-body inline-block mt-8 underline","style":{"color":"#D22C2E","fontSize":"0.9rem"},"children":"← All articles"}]]}]}]
